* TRY THIS:  The End -- Or the Beginning 

As you can probably see, the Internet is simultaneously a vast 
jumble of disorganized data and random stuff, an incomparable 
resource, and a marvelous source of entertainment.  The trick is 
to learn how to "work the dashboard" and to find the resources, 
services and people of interest to you!


