The Delphi Holiday Gopher includes holiday-related recipes, books, 
stories, songs, music, graphics, holiday items, and gift ideas, plus 
road condition and weather report/forecast information.  (FYI, according 
to Delphi, the information has all been checked before including it; 
everything is "G" rated and suitable for the entire family.) 

From Delphi, enter

    GO ENT HOLIDAY <RETURN>

(You'll also find some options available to Delphi users only, including 
Delphi's own "Send a Letter to Santa.") 

From World, MV, IDS or other Internet sites, enter 

    gopher delphi.com <RETURN>


